Exception handling

try {

	// any code that might throw exception(s)
}
catch(.1.) {
	// here we have to take care of exception
	// log the exception(into text file, xml file, json file)
}
catch(.2.) {
		// here we have to take care of exception
	// log the exception(into text file, xml file, json file)
}
finally {
	// close other resources 
}


throw
throws --> we can omit the try..catch blocks if your method 
throws the exception

User Defined Exception

class MyException extends Exception {

}

